The paper discusses intrusion detection systems and anomaly detection systems, which are commonly used in the field of computer security (cs.CR). The focus of the paper is on detecting anomalies in network traffic, which falls under the category of network infrastructure (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for anomaly detection (cs.AI), and the challenges of scalability and false alarms (cs.LG, cs.SI).
